2.title: Request
2.query:
fetch logs
| filter `k8s.deployment.name` == "gitlab-webservice-default"
| parse content, "JSON:contentjson"
| filter contentjson[component] == "gitlab"
| makeTimeseries count(), by: toString(contentjson[status])

3.title: Access Log
3.query:
fetch logs
| filter `k8s.deployment.name` == "gitlab-webservice-default"
| parse content, "JSON:contentjson"
| fieldsFlatten contentjson
| filter contentjson.component == "gitlab"
| filter contentjson.status == 200
| fields contentjson.meta.user, contentjson.meta.user_id, contentjson.path, contentjson.remote_ip

6.title: Error Log
6.query:
fetch `logs`
| filter k8s.namespace.name == "gitlab"
| parse content, "JSON:contentjson"
| fieldsFlatten contentjson
| fieldsKeep timestamp, k8s.container.name, contentjson.uri
| limit 20

7.title: Access / Project
7.query:
fetch `logs`
| filter k8s.namespace.name == "gitlab"
| parse content, "JSON:contentjson"
| fieldsFlatten contentjson
| makeTimeseries count(), by: contentjson[meta.project]

8.title: Projects total
8.query:
fetch logs
| filter `k8s.deployment.name` == "gitlab-webservice-default"
| parse content, "JSON:contentjson"
| fieldsFlatten contentjson
| fieldsKeep contentjson.meta.project 
| summarize countDistinct(contentjson.meta.project)

9.title: Groups

fetch logs
| filter `k8s.deployment.name` == "gitlab-webservice-default"
| parse content, "JSON:contentjson"
| fieldsFlatten contentjson
| fieldsKeep contentjson.meta.group

11.query:

13.query:
fetch dt.entity.container_group
| filter startsWith(entity.name, "gitlab-side")
| filter entity.name == "gitlab-sidekiq-all-in-*-v*-*"

15.title: Requests / min
15.query:
fetch logs
| filter `k8s.deployment.name` == "gitlab-webservice-default"
| parse content, "JSON:contentjson"
| filter contentjson[component] == "gitlab"
| summarize count()
